<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Dishonourable" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Dishonourable,</orth> destitute of honour, shameful: <bibl n="shak. r2 4.65" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.2.26" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 2, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 1, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.1.76" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 1, 76</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 1.2.138" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 2, 138</bibl>.<lb />Adverbially: <cit><quote>more d. ragged than an old faced ancient,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.2.33" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 2, 33</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>